&lt;p&gt;In this role, you&#39;ll architect data-driven growth strategies that deliver predictable, scalable pipeline generation. You&#39;ll own the analytical frameworks that measure complex, multi-touch customer journeys and optimize channel performance. This is an opportunity to apply performance marketing rigor to enterprise B2B growth for a company at the forefront of responsible AI development.&lt;/p&gt;
