&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Channel Strategy &amp;amp; Execution: Own strategic development and tactical execution of SEO, paid media (LinkedIn, Google, 6sense/ABM platforms), and lifecycle marketing programs. Identify, evaluate, and test new channels to diversify acquisition strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ICP Targeting &amp;amp; Optimization: Develop sophisticated targeting strategies to reach ICPs across channels, provide platform-specific creative guidance, and collaborate to improve MQL signals and campaign efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytics &amp;amp; Measurement: Partner with Data Science teams to guide attribution models and measurement frameworks. Define KPIs, interpret complex data, and communicate performance insights to stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lifecycle &amp;amp; Growth: Identify opportunities for lead nurturing and account expansion, optimizing customer journey progression and conversion funnels across multiple touchpoints&lt;/li&gt;
