&lt;li&gt;Analytical Excellence: Strong analytical mindset with ability to interpret complex data, guide measurement frameworks, and translate insights into scalable strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Channel Expertise: Experience with account-based marketing platforms, multi-touch attribution, and optimization of sophisticated conversion funnels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stakeholder Management: Exceptional communication skills with experience influencing cross-functional teams and presenting complex performance data to senior leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
