&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vertical industry expertise with demonstrated success marketing to specific enterprise sectors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with AI/ML products or emerging technology categories&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with advanced analytics platforms and marketing automation systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of implementing ABM at enterprise scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background building marketing programs for new product categories&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
