&lt;p&gt;You will own &quot;data as the product&quot; for our most critical AI research initiatives, translating cutting-edge research needs into robust, scalable data collection systems. This role requires the technical depth to understand complex AI systems combined with the strategic mindset to build and scale operations that support frontier model development.&lt;/p&gt;
