&lt;li&gt;Have 8+ years of progressive accounting and financial reporting experience, with at least 3 years in a leadership role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess deep expertise in US GAAP and have experience with both AICPA and SEC reporting standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have hands-on experience leading Workiva implementations and optimizing the platform for financial reporting workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are proficient with multiple ERP systems, particularly NetSuite and either Oracle Fusion or Workday Financials&lt;/li&gt;
